a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"38e14a543b537965405c2bcde0fdef0408a60475","tid":1667070,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcc00112dc08d77c105811086cdf5b8038931ac9","tid":1667070,"uid":39682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"已經課左，幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732b97f9aa349e79c77aecf2ef549efd44ce039b","tid":1667070,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:21:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8712520635dd0eca038e01d01f2f0fb80c398de9","tid":1667070,"uid":288116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:23:17.000Z","msg":"已課，幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8338cc7337e84ec301c2075788546702eacf4528","tid":1667070,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36bf51976bbe40d7f56ec55b4492a38e14d4aa7","tid":1667070,"uid":289649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"25e0fd87e68d14500ac6d4fcb9428dd72587b7a7","tid":1667070,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c479a2e2df84c17124e9784e28699f73dc6f90","tid":1667070,"uid":48667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:29:56.000Z","msg":"push <br />\n仲有大專學界嗰個"},{"pid":"6e477bbc2f30f8c1b835c18a0202c31f4e8c0d11","tid":1667070,"uid":197989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"已課 推"},{"pid":"e8568fed62309fbcc55e8e7aa4fc3933f24c2564","tid":1667070,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"ccc1a89d9b75434ae21e3b3930642dcd5648e25f","tid":1667070,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25744781dbbef475a02564620022ced5ce8cb36","tid":1667070,"uid":158186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:41:47.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b7245fbd2debb0956e85c690c216c88dd66f11","tid":1667070,"uid":296705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"課左"},{"pid":"8248160f9f59a59d1820e1a2661cd85dd7f6ad6c","tid":1667070,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2c4692c66d81d6d14e66cb8b36eefff51b3dd5","tid":1667070,"uid":149008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd61efb1d01cb7619657bcc42f867ea44a8fc5f","tid":1667070,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d07c80ec42bee3747be0821e98717703a4075b5","tid":1667070,"uid":64278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"一早課左"},{"pid":"9c6a05b2035383986530c32287630cba2a8b923c","tid":1667070,"uid":58896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:09:17.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n利申：已課（不過月